Package: IOBRportal
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny-Based Platform for Bulk Transcriptome and Immuno-Oncology Analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Description: IOBRportal is an R package and Shiny-based platform for bulk transcriptome and immuno-oncology analysis. It integrates data preprocessing, signature score calculation, tumor microenvironment deconvolution, statistical analysis, visualization, mutation analysis, and cohort-oriented workflows into a unified analysis environment.
Maintainer: Qingcong Luo <qingcongl@163.com>, Dongqiang Zeng <interlaken@smu.edu.cn>
License: GPL-3
